				<div class="et_pb_text_inner" data-et-multi-view="{&quot;schema&quot;:{&quot;content&quot;:{&quot;desktop&quot;:&quot;&lt;h6 style=\&quot;text-align: left;\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=\&quot;color: #c14953; font-size: medium;\&quot;&gt;No &lt;\/span&gt;&lt;span style=\&quot;font-size: medium;\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\&quot;color: #383838;\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\&quot;color: #c14953;\&quot;&gt;1 in Malaysia&lt;\/span&gt;&lt;\/span&gt;&lt;\/span&gt;&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/h6&gt;\n&lt;h6 style=\&quot;text-align: left;\&quot;&gt;#Architecture\/ Built Environment&lt;\/h6&gt;\n&lt;h6 style=\&quot;text-align: left;\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=\&quot;font-size: medium;\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\&quot;color: #383838;\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\&quot;color: #c14953;\&quot;&gt;&lt;br \/&gt;Top 50 in The World&lt;\/span&gt;&lt;\/span&gt;&lt;\/span&gt;&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/h6&gt;\n&lt;h6 style=\&quot;text-align: left;\&quot;&gt;#Petroleum Engineering&lt;\/h6&gt;\n&lt;h6 style=\&quot;text-align: left;\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=\&quot;font-size: medium;\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\&quot;color: #383838;\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\&quot;color: #c14953;\&quot;&gt;&lt;br \/&gt;Top 100 in the World&lt;\/span&gt;&lt;\/span&gt;&lt;\/span&gt;&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/h6&gt;\n&lt;h6 style=\&quot;text-align: left;\&quot;&gt;#Architecture\/Built Environment&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;#Data Science and Artificial Intelligence&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;#Engineering &#8211; Mineral &amp; Mining&lt;\/h6&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;h6 style=\&quot;text-align: left;\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\&quot;font-size: small;\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\&quot;color: #c19100;\&quot;&gt;2025\u00a0QS WORLD UNIVERSITY RANKINGS &lt;\/span&gt;&lt;\/span&gt;&lt;span style=\&quot;font-size: small;\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\&quot;color: #c19100;\&quot;&gt;BY SUBJECTS&lt;\/span&gt;&lt;\/span&gt;&lt;\/h6&gt;&quot;,&quot;tablet&quot;:&quot;&lt;h6&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;No 1 in Malaysia&lt;\/span&gt;&lt;\/span&gt;&lt;\/span&gt;&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/h6&gt;\n&lt;h6&gt;#Architecture\/ Built Environment&lt;\/h6&gt;\n&lt;h6&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Top 100 in the World&lt;\/span&gt;&lt;\/span&gt;&lt;\/span&gt;&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/h6&gt;\n&lt;h6&gt;#Engineering-Mineral &amp; Mining&lt;\/h6&gt;\n&lt;h6&gt;#Architecture\/ Built Environment&lt;\/h6&gt;\n&lt;h6&gt;#Engineering-Civil &amp; Structural&lt;\/h6&gt;\n&lt;h6&gt;#Engineering-Petroleum&lt;\/h6&gt;\n&lt;h6&gt;#Engineering-Electrical and Electronics&lt;\/h6&gt;\n&lt;h6&gt;#Engineering-Chemical&lt;\/h6&gt;\n&lt;h6&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Top 150&lt;\/span&gt;&lt;\/span&gt;&lt;\/span&gt;&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/h6&gt;\n&lt;h6&gt;#Engineering-Mechanical, Aeronautical &amp; Manufacturing&lt;\/h6&gt;\n&lt;h6&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span&gt;QS WORLD UNIVERSITY RANKINGS &lt;\/span&gt;&lt;\/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;BY SUBJECTS 2024&lt;\/span&gt;&lt;\/span&gt;&lt;\/h6&gt;&quot;}},&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;et_pb_text&quot;}" data-et-multi-view-load-tablet-hidden="true"><h6 style="text-align: left;"><strong><span style="color: #c14953; font-size: medium;">No </span><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #383838;"><span style="color: #c14953;">1 in Malaysia</span></span></span></strong></h6>
<h6 style="text-align: left;">#Architecture/ Built Environment</h6>
<h6 style="text-align: left;"><strong><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #383838;"><span style="color: #c14953;"><br />Top 50 in The World</span></span></span></strong></h6>
<h6 style="text-align: left;">#Petroleum Engineering</h6>
<h6 style="text-align: left;"><strong><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #383838;"><span style="color: #c14953;"><br />Top 100 in the World</span></span></span></strong></h6>
